FBIS3-12170 "drnes039_l_94022" FBIS-NES-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 ISRAEL Prime Minister Rabin Reacts to Hebron Incident Compares Killer to Hamas, Islamic Jihad TA2702190994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1800 GMT 27 Feb 94 TA2702190994 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Prime Minister Rabin made a comment about the massacre a short time ago in an address to the International Jewish Media Conference in Jerusalem. [Begin Rabin recording] So far, we know that he did it on his own but I am also ashamed about others that came out publicly and supported his act. I believe that they represent a very small number of the people of Israel, even a small number among the settlers that oppose the policy of the present Government of Israel. He tried not just to kill innocent Palestinians while they were praying in a holy place. He joined with the Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] and the Islamic Jihad in the purpose to kill the peace negotiations. [end recording]
